Title: I'll Defeat Freeza! Another Super Saiyan
Writer: Takao Koyama, Aya Matsui, Hiroshi Toda
Actors: Masako Nozawa, Mayumi Tanaka, Hiromi Tsuru
Plot: The bone-chilling onslaught of Frieza and King Cold is brought to a halt by a mysterious stranger with a mighty sword, but only time will tell if this new warrior is friend or foe!
